°What This Is

About
GSF is a modular digital ecosystem designed for compliance‑first community and educational tools in trading.  
It focuses on architecture that scales from core components to a full user platform.
    °Why This Matters
Purpose
Retail traders often lack structured spaces to learn, document, and grow without regulatory issues.  
GSF provides infrastructure for community, education, and future modules without economy custody or investment advice.
   
°MVP Scope (What We Plan First)

MVP Focus (30–60 Days)
- Auth & profiles
- Community posts + moderation
- Trading journal (manual entry)
- Static education modules
- Compliance layer (no advice, no signals)
     
